{"id": "1202974520420339732", "channel_id": "1202974520420339732", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "在电脑上使用模拟器游玩看统统消失的描述说明都有点费眼睛，在手机上玩就更费眼睛了。快出一个长按可以放大描述说明的功能吧，以后说明机制更复杂说明更长就更需要了！！！", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T13:51:15.854000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1202974521641009232", "filename": "IMG_7749.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 7151824, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202974520420339732/1202974521641009232/IMG_7749.png?ex=6a008d54&is=69ff3bd4&hm=7eddbfd6ac6ba3d1f3eb9edd24b182b8b75d39f6e81a7758f9ff7ba8cd739e73&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202974520420339732", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于指令卡描述小作文的说明", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1202889508438282351", "channel_id": "1202889508438282351", "type": 0, "author_id": "1189415892166131765", "author_name": "taoziguojiang", "author_bot": false, "content": "最近很多活动，限时还无扫荡，过年没时间肝了，看到还剩20天感觉有点难受，已通过的难度可以加上扫荡吗😅", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T08:13:27.418000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202889508438282351", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」活动很多，但是限时且无扫荡", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1203066783259697203", "channel_id": "1203066783259697203", "type": 0, "author_id": "1137328302135181312", "author_name": "cra0261_", "author_bot": false, "content": "具體是這五個，特別是後面四個永久的\n感覺有點累贅了", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T19:57:53.029000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-02-02T19:58:31.824000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1203066783653826691", "filename": "IMG_4275.png", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 502575, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1203066783259697203/1203066783653826691/IMG_4275.png?ex=6a003a81&is=69fee901&hm=a8846ed6b567ab5670cdffd7d838f5641e88fd88ff76840ab338f8f23037212d&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1203066783259697203", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」建議考慮一下在活動面板中移除已完成的活動", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1202971807909679124", "channel_id": "1202971807909679124", "type": 0, "author_id": "968857106985910302", "author_name": "enosred", "author_bot": false, "content": "举个例子：\n         戈利亚的大招会给巨刃之威。丽兹的绿炎会在下个回合升级为腐化绿炎，有了启灵之后腐化绿炎后续还会升级成死灭绿炎。\n         目前除了进入某种模式在战斗过程中查看之外，在局外没有其他方法可以查看巨刃之威、腐化绿炎、死灭绿炎的方法。\n         解决方法有两种：\n         一种是对于特殊的角色增加一个记录自己衍生卡或者其他效果的栏目。比如戈利亚的巨刃之威、丽兹的xx绿炎、詹金的鼠群冲击等。还有一些比如希洛三启会拿到的不规则形态，这种衍生卡建议是也收集在这个栏目里。\n         一种是在局外推出一个类似于图鉴的功能，用来收录命轮的功能描述、造物、刻印、症状卡、状态卡，也增加一个栏目用来收录这些少数角色才有的衍生卡。", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T13:40:29.141000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1202971809545199646", "filename": "IMG_7747.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 6544943, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202971807909679124/1202971809545199646/IMG_7747.png?ex=6a008acd&is=69ff394d&hm=f7207b18a4aef19e6787cb124cda1df98b0d619959082cf7cc7bc16eafed1184&"}, {"id": "1202971810908471407", "filename": "IMG_7748.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 7111202, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202971807909679124/1202971810908471407/IMG_7748.png?ex=6a008acd&is=69ff394d&hm=840659beb422833d1d568262f5fb0ddc99dd1af39398248f02c3179a6cb6b152&"}, {"id": "1202971812040937534", "filename": "IMG_7750.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 6734386, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202971807909679124/1202971812040937534/IMG_7750.png?ex=6a008ace&is=69ff394e&hm=ff5d1e03c9161d282fedc027082b07742105436028512fe94cdd41981bcda65a&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202971807909679124", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」关于唤醒体衍生卡的说明", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
