{"id": "1202875516508442634", "channel_id": "1202875516508442634", "type": 0, "author_id": "197895857390092288", "author_name": "vir1eo", "author_bot": false, "content": "......一路用深海玩到55連個觸腕次數都過不了\n誰想要一樣的東西重複強迫性打那麼多次啊\n更不用說還要四界\n還沒過年哪有這麼多閒時間\n拜託企劃自己也肝完整個活動獎勵\n下次設計的時候才不會這麼離譜", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T07:17:51.482000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202875516508442634", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」故事的魔法活動中成就獎勵門檻過高", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
{"id": "1202832964715806740", "channel_id": "1202832964715806740", "type": 0, "author_id": "371624648078524416", "author_name": "devis0212", "author_bot": false, "content": "希望助戰能有獨立的設定命輪以及密契 我不知道我拔掉換別隻之後助戰的角色會不會跟著被拔掉", "timestamp": "2024-02-02T04:28:46.344000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}], "attachments": [{"id": "1202832965730697236", "filename": "IMG_8638.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 6922835, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1202832964715806740/1202832965730697236/IMG_8638.png?ex=6a00b23e&is=69ff60be&hm=7d645270ed4768c0b91bb810a8ef7a765d3c5f664f51378e8d283cdc925e1104&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1202832964715806740", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」助戰角色", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
